{"tid":346302,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街iphone耳機累撚死我","createTime":"2017-08-03T22:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T06:49:45.000Z","uid":103380,"like":466,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b98ca8b5b6e81b2ff0dcb5936808609905abd9d","tid":346302,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:26:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n頭先3點幾 我見屋企人訓哂<br />\n係床到用手機睇AV<br />\n咁咪戴iphone耳機聽<br />\n睇左差唔多成個鐘<br />\n睇到興恰恰 突然feel到有對眼 望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來我老母起床黎望住我 <br />\n好彩唔係o係被竇打緊飛機<br />\n不過都冇咩所謂 因為都冇分別！<br />\n<br />\n我除低個耳機問我老母：「咁夜唔訓望住我做乜」<br />\n除低個下就知奶野 <br />\n較左一半多啲咁大聲加上三更半夜好撚靜<br />\n<br />\n我播AV啲聲傳撚哂出黎 <br />\n係放低耳機都聽到個隻<br />\n<br />\n我播左成個鐘頭 係咁 呀～呀～呀～<br />\n<br />\n橫死掂死 我係我老母話我：「傻左呀？」之前我截佢糊<br />\n<br />\n「唉得啦，我冇野做。」<br />\n<br />\n我老母就返左房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁想問下連登仔意見我仲繼唔繼續睇好？<br />\n<br />\n睇，反正老母冇理，叫埋佢睇仲得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好聽，嘈住人訓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435c905f746e4a06f94fa8ebf3c3a07cd5488191","tid":346302,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:38:41.000Z","msg":"繼續睇"},{"pid":"c190db9a91f64d06f2fb635076f24668c87abfd1","tid":346302,"uid":45773,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:40:51.000Z","msg":"反正佢都聽到，直接連落大喇叭睇啦"},{"pid":"3f515137df4aae24e5d88b5c46a057ce8c5f51a7","tid":346302,"uid":72638,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:41:38.000Z","msg":"伯有幾十歲人 有咩未見過"},{"pid":"d4da4261376d76e9a80651c510c1cbc119a6fbdc","tid":346302,"uid":10859,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:43:09.000Z","msg":"心諗個垃圾仔冇出色<br />\n冇女要自己打飛機"},{"pid":"d3a8eafc339de92dafe55d60544b7e53430472f5","tid":346302,"uid":103380,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:44:17.000Z","